divs: sighting detailsthis is a summation of thre seperate observations links to my youtube records of the events...including illustrations and video, and photos *(links moved to additional evidence section--cms\sg). additional information- i'd estimate altitude at 3000 ft based on location above cumulus clouds. i was walking my dog the object\ contrails were huge and impossible to ignore. i cant explain what could cause these sharp angles in contrails. i felt excitement and interest and curiosity and amazement and a sense of adventure and fun. i lost sight becuase the sun set and it became dark.
